SYNOPSIS

    In your weaver.ini:

     [-Sort::Sub]

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin is used when building distribution that contains
    Sort::Sub::* routines (see Sort::Sub::naturally for an example of such
    module; see also Sort::Sub). It currently does the following to
    lib/Sort/Sub/* .pm files:

      * Add Synopsis section if not already exists

      * Add description about the module to Description section

      * Mention some modules in See Also section

      e.g. Sort::Sub.

SEE ALSO

    Sort::Sub

